                             'Geodesik' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Geodesik' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to 'grow'
crystals toward the center of a geode-like structure, so they are
all of the same size. Crystals can be of 4 sizes: short, medium,
tall and tallest. As you grow one crystal, another crystal may
randomly increase or decrease in size...

  There are 4 types of geodes, each with their own level of crystal
stability; from a very high stability (which will be easier to
complete), to a very low stability, which will make you 'battle'
for awhile with some pesky crystals...

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

